    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>[Congressional Record Volume 163, Number 1 (Tuesday, January 3, 2017)]From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Ms. BROWNLEY of California:H.R. 108.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Amendment XVI.[Page H49]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
